  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Coals to Gunpowder</h1>\n  <br/>\n  <p>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Release-2.14.x-limegreen\" alt=\"Release\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.16.x%2026.1.x-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,&logoWidth=50\" alt=\"Minecraft\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/License-CC_BY_4.0-blueviolet\" alt=\"License CC BY 4.0\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Tq83Zuhduv\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1358706268012810350?color=5865F2&label=Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\">\n    </a>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/NkWAhtTT?logo=modrinth&label=Modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<br/>\n<br/>\n\n<h2>✨ Features</h2>\n<h3>🔥 Main description</h3>\n<blockquote>This feature allows players to convert charcoal or coal into gunpowder using a furnace or blast furnace. <br/>It introduces a new way to obtain this essential resource using more accessible materials.</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚙️ Use and benefits</h3>\n<blockquote>With this process, players can produce gunpowder without relying solely on mobs or rare discoveries. <br/>It makes progression smoother and gives more control over crafting explosive or useful items.</blockquote>\n\n<h3>🧩 Gameplay integration</h3>\n<blockquote>This system fits naturally into existing mechanics by using familiar blocks. <br/>It encourages experimentation and resource management while expanding crafting possibilities.</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>🧪 Recipes</h2>\n<h3>🔲 Input</h3>\n<blockquote><b><img src=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/icon/coal.png\"> Coal <br/><img src=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/icon/charcoal.png\"> Charcoal</b></blockquote>\n<h3>🔥 Smelted in</h3>\n<blockquote><b><img src=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/icon/furnace.png\"> Furnace <br/><img src=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/icon/blast_furnace.png\"> Blast Furnace</b></blockquote>\n<h3>🎁 Output</h3>\n<blockquote><b><img src=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/icon/gunpowder.png\"> Gunpowder</b></blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>📥 Installation</h2>\n<h3>📁 Datapack</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.zip</code> file into your world's <code>datapacks</code> folder.<br/>\n  Reload the world or use <code>/reload</code>.<br/>\n  Enjoy your enchanted adventure!\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚙️ Mod</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.jar</code> file into the <code>mods</code> folder of your instance.<br/>\n  <code>Restart</code> your game.<br/>\n  Have fun!\n</blockquote>",
